3.11	Battle_of_Mikatagahara	Battle of Mikatagahara	The Battle of Mikatagahara Mikatagahara no tatakai) (January, 1573; Tōtōmi Province, Japan) was one of the most famous battles of Takeda Shingen's campaigns, and one of the best demonstrations of his cavalry-based tactics.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/85/Mikatagahara_no_tatakai.jpg/300px-Mikatagahara_no_tatakai.jpg
